info.name: Phantom Forces theme for Roblox
info.description: (This theme took me around 6 and a half hours before the first release!) Do you like playing the Phantom Forces game on Roblox? I've been playing it for around a month now and I can't stop enjoying it! What about the Roblox website themed as Phantom Forces? There you have it! A background image which is an artwork by exelar, the game logo when your browser page is big, the same in-game Roblox cursor and a base of my other dark Roblox theme! Install it today and send me your feedback!
info.additionalInfo: Here are cool facts to know about this theme! When you have a bigger screen, the Roblox logo is changed by a Phantom Forces logo, which was traced by me from a screen capture! Even though I started this theme with my other theme (DarkBlox)'s CSS code, it took me from 9 A.M. to 4 P.M.! All CSS edits, one per one, were tested in Chrome DevTools then saved to this theme. I even lost 30 lines of code because I hadn't saved!
